{"tid":1359491,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超2019/20賽季【罰球】規則改動","createTime":"2019-07-24T06:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T10:04:58.000Z","uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8f1f54b0db6f885b642be053bde5e7bef755ee71","tid":1359491,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:54:43.000Z","msg":"#PL 英超2019/20賽季【罰球】規則改動：<br />\n<br />\n1️⃣ 守方排出3人及以上人牆時，攻方球員須離人牆1碼以上；<br />\n<br />\n2️⃣ 球員可在本方禁區內接門將開出的龍門球和罰球；<br />\n<br />\n3️⃣ 攻方可選擇快開罰球，球證將在下次死球時再向守方球員出牌；但假如球證出牌已經影響比賽進程，則攻方不能快開罰球；攻方明顯入球機會被守方犯規破壞時，如果攻方選擇快開罰球，守方原本因犯規被出示的紅牌將降為黃牌。"},{"pid":"ce9cf654f8238d5e9f77fa280fb8c4bb41e0bde8","tid":1359491,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:54:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/414854688592788/posts/2452927791452124?s=709798201&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F414854688592788%2Fposts%2F2452927791452124%3Fs%3D709798201%26sfns%3Dmo&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTeylkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=33834581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/414854688592788/posts/2452927791452124?s=709798201&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"87bd2756222aac554f26427270c74f49b6baab84","tid":1359491,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:58:50.000Z","msg":"第三<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8742b154a3785a8cc6e3bf90b3f48e1f20812c68","tid":1359491,"uid":147367,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"點改英超啲球證都係鳩吹架啦"},{"pid":"6377a917d120e96c6c5d171433a674c89d4742c6","tid":1359491,"uid":72334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:12:20.000Z","msg":"下季係咪有var喇？"},{"pid":"e1ff8d